  "blurb": "The full beachfront residence estate at Lipa Noi on Koh Samui’s west coast — a collection of Ayutthaya-style pavilioned villas taken together, with sweeping lawns running to a quiet, swimmable beach and multiple pools framing the Gulf. Ideal for large families, multi-generational gatherings, weddings and events, fully staffed throughout. Price on request.",
  "detail": "For the largest celebrations, the entire beachfront estate at Lipa Noi can be taken as one — a collection of Ayutthaya-inspired pavilioned villas sharing a single pristine stretch of west-coast Koh Samui, with manicured gardens running down to a quiet, swimmable white-sand beach and some of the island’s finest sunsets across the Gulf.\n\nCombined, the residences sleep large groups across many en-suite bedrooms, with multiple pools — including infinity and waterfall pools — sun decks, beach salas and generous indoor and outdoor living and dining spaces. It is purpose-made for multi-generational holidays, reunions, weddings and corporate retreats, with the flexibility to scale the number of villas to your party.\n\nThe estate is fully staffed and managed — villa managers, private chefs, daily breakfast and housekeeping — with gyms, saunas, jacuzzis and in-villa spa treatments available, plus event support, private parking and Wi-Fi throughout. A short drive from Nathon and the island’s dining and amenities. Rates and configuration are tailored to each booking; price on request.",
